{{item:3056}} {{item:3056}} {{item:3056}} 

Today riot got rid of zephyr, an outlier of an item that I really loved. Combo-ing this with boots of swiftness was always a lot of fun and the only way to maximise slow resist and tenacity. Now it has gone and they sort of alluded to the fact their eyes are turning towards Ohmwrecker&#039;s extinction order 66. THIS. MUST NOT HAPPEN.

Ohmwrecker is another favourite item of mine and a unique item unlike any other at the moment. Again not many people use it and this fact I liked because I believe it to be a hidden op. Silent I am no more however. Deadman&#039;s plate and Ohmwrecker give huge amounts of movement speed (especially around towers). This is invaluable to any tank that is prone to being kited. In more than one case I&#039;ve saved helpless allies getting tower aggro with the active. In a more aggressive build it also works a treat. Ohmwrecker allows you to build damage, but still be more than decent at tower diving. Bruiser builds really benefit from this item. Another point I might add is that Ohmwrecker is currently the only item in the game that gives a combination of health, armour AND cdr. A tank could not ask for more.

Brethren, I am gathering support here today to save a future execution of this item. Use this item and try it out, is all I ask and with a bit of luck this will gain popularity. You will not be disappointed.

